## Healthcare Disclaimer

This software is designed for educational and informational purposes only. 
It is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, 
diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or other 
qualified health provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical 
condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it 
because of something you have read in this software.

The AI assistant (Lez) is designed to provide general health information and 
guidance, but should never be used as a replacement for professional medical 
consultation. In case of medical emergencies, always contact your local 
emergency services immediately.

## Data Privacy Notice

This software handles sensitive health information. Users and implementers 
must ensure compliance with applicable healthcare privacy regulations 
including but not limited to HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and 
Accountability Act) in the United States and similar regulations in other 
jurisdictions.

The software includes features for:
- Secure handling of Protected Health Information (PHI)
- Encrypted data storage and transmission
- User consent management
- Data access controls

However, proper implementation and configuration of security measures is the 
responsibility of the deploying organization.